	* scanBuildLog: %[ER: 71]% minor changes to be able to scan
	  logfiles created with rub

2005-05-03 09:12  loose

	* rub1: %[ER: 70]%

	  Sometimes, but not always, cvs has a return status 1 when update
	  conflicts occur. If this happens, the recursive call of rub1
	  fails and rub does not get the chance to report the update
	  conflict. Hence, I moved the check and diagnostics from rub into
	  rub1.

