	* variants.lofar17: %[ER: 71]% changed aipspath in iccbuilds to
	  lofarbuild version

2005-01-21 15:38  lofar

	* makedep.sh: %[ER:71]% Script to make all package tree files and
	  html pages that show LOFAR dependencies

2005-01-19 15:04  loose

	* variants.lofar17: %[ER: 30]%

	  If desired, ccache can now be used when compiling sources. To do
	  so, you must let the environment variable CCACHE point to the
	  ccache executable program.

