	  preprocessor defines

2005-01-13 13:48  loose

	* lofar_dtl.m4: %[ER: 30]%

	  The variable lfr_option in the second call of lofar_external()
	  was "accidentally" clobbered by the first call of
	  lofar_external() -- ALL variables are global! Hence, the variable
	  name was changed to lfr_dtl_option in order to make it unique.

2005-01-13 13:46  zwart

	* lofar_aips++.m4: %[ER: 222]%

	  Changed the place where search paths are defined (to make it work
	  with casa)

