	* lofar_aips++.m4: %[ER: 222]%

	  Changed to make it work with casa rpms and casapath environment
	  variable

2005-01-10 11:41  diepen

	* lofar_aips++.m4: %[ER: 70]% Add 2nd argument giving the libraries

2005-01-07 11:41  diepen

	* variants.lofar9: %[ER: 222]% Use weekly AIPS++

2005-01-07 08:56  diepen

	* variants.lofar17: %[ER: 222]% Use AIPS++ casa namespace

2005-01-06 18:02  loose

	* lofar_general.m4, lofar_shmem.m4, variants: %[ER: 177]%

	  Shared memory can now be enabled or disabled using
	  --with-shmem=[yes|no] during configure. Furthermore,
	  --with-shmem=yes has been made the default for the standard
	  variant (e.g. debug, opt, mpich, etc.); the bgl and fakebgl
	  variants use --with-shmem=no by default.

2005-01-03 14:09  romein

	* lofar_external.m4, variants.node08: %[ER:220]% Several changes on
	  behalf of x86_64 architecture.

2005-01-03 09:56  diepen

	* finddep: %[ER: 70]% Added -all files

2004-12-29 15:39  loose

