	  for g++

2002-05-13 14:03  wierenga

	* crontab.builds: Added new make targets.

	  Default rule (all) now calls the build target.  For daily and
	  weekly builds new rules have been added (daily, weekly).

	  Normal interactive use of the toplevel Makefile would be:

		  make bootstrap	  # bootstrap and configure all
	  variants

		  make			  # make all variants (equiv. to
	  make build)

		  make rebuild		  # clean and build all variants

2002-05-13 10:07  gvd

	* lofar_init.m4: Always add -Wno-unknown-pragmas to CXXFLAGS (for
	  DMI compilations)

2002-05-13 09:54  wierenga

	* lofarconf: I accidentally had a LOFAR/LOFAR/BaseSim dir which was
	  messing up lofarconf.  The fix is no longer needed.

