2002-04-09 16:25  wierenga

	* crontab.builds: crontab for running daily and weekly builds.

2002-03-26 11:50  gvd

	* lofar_aips++.m4, lofar_basesim.m4, lofar_corba.m4,
	  lofar_matlab.m4, lofar_mpi.m4, lofar_qatools.m4, lofar_xerces.m4:
	  Add -I to CPPFLAGS instead of C(XX)FLAGS otherwise *.i cannot be
	  made

