	* lofar_mpi.m4: Revert to previous version

2002-01-30 13:32  gvd

	* lofar_mpi.m4: -lmpe is needed for profiler

2001-12-21 10:39  gvd

	* Makefile.common, lofar_docxx.m4: Added DOCDIR variable in make
	  doc and docthis

2001-12-20 09:05  gvd

	* Makefile.common, lofar_basesim.m4, lofar_docxx.m4, lofar_init.m4:
	  Added lofar_init.m4 Improved lofar_basesim in detection of
	  BaseSim library Added support for doxygen in lofar_docxx.m4

2001-12-07 14:31  gvd

	* lofar_puretools.m4: lofar_puretools.m4 has been renamed to
	  lofar_qatools.m4

2001-12-07 14:30  gvd

	* Makefile.common, bootstrap, insuretool, lofar_aips++.m4,
	  lofar_basesim.m4, lofar_corba.m4, lofar_debugoptimise.m4,
	  lofar_docxx.m4, lofar_matlab.m4, lofar_mpi.m4, lofar_qatools.m4,
	  makeshadow, makeshadowcopy, puretool: Added support for insure,
	  doc++ Added compiler options like -Wall Improved detection of
	  BaseSim Fixed for Solaris and for newer autotools versions

2001-11-07 15:08  wierenga

	* lofar_debugoptimise.m4: Renamed --with-optimise to
	  --with-optimize (american english spelling).

2001-11-07 15:00  wierenga

	* lofar_mpi.m4: Removed --enable-mpi directive. To use MPI simply
	  specify either --with-mpich or --with-scampi.

2001-11-07 14:48  wierenga

	* lofar_basesim.m4: Added --with-basesim option to configure. If
	  you don't specify this option configure will try to find the
	  BaseSim dir in the following way. If you run configure from
	  LOFAR/LOFARSim/build/optimize for example, it will look in
	  LOFAR/BaseSim/src for BaseSim header files and in
	  LOFAR/BaseSim/build/optimize for BaseSim libraries. You can
	  override this default location where configure looks for BaseSim
	  by specifying e.g.
	  --with-basesim=/home/user/cvs/LOFAR/BaseSim/build.

2001-10-31 12:34  wierenga

	* bootstrap, lofar_aips++.m4, lofar_basesim.m4, lofar_corba.m4,
	  lofar_matlab.m4: LOFAR CVS Repository structure change and
	  transition to autotools (autoconf, automake and libtool).

2001-10-26 12:06  wierenga

	* bootstrap, puretool, run-configure, lofar_aips++.m4,
	  lofar_corba.m4, lofar_debugoptimise.m4, lofar_firewalls.m4,
	  lofar_matlab.m4, lofar_mpi.m4, lofar_puretools.m4: Wide spread
	  changes to convert from Makedefs to autoconf/automake/libtool
	  build environment

